The paper deals with recommendation and ranking tasks, which are commonly studied in the information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) communities. The specific applications mentioned in the abstract, image annotation (cs.CV) and music recommendation (cs.MM), also suggest these categories. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing techniques (cs.CL) in the experiments.
